name: Starry For Cash
description:
Do you want to plant your own tree and get rewards?
Plant your own tree under the beautiful starry sky,The brand new planting game is here!
Plant your own tree in the planting game!


Plant a tree that belongs to you,make your pocket rich and cultivate the richest wood in the world in the tree planting app!
You can grow plants by tapping vigorously in the game like a real capitalist get more rewards!


In the process of planting trees, you can also use props or fertilization to make plants grow faster.


Drop everything that bothers you, start a tree that belongs to you! Make nature more expensive, and let you in the game rich growth!


You are one step away from being rich!
Are you ready to build a tree of your own?
Enjoy the feedback from nature!
Let your tree grow fast!
